name: Alien Jumps!
description:
This game is about an alien named Freddy travelling through the galaxy when suddenly his spaceship stopped working and broke and he fell down on a planet and lost consciousness. When he woke up, there was a hologram in front of him. He told Freddy about his planet and the way out of the it was to parkour. Now you, yes I'm taking to you. You have to help Freddy get out of this place by parkouring and surviving cute deadly animals.

NOTE: THIS GAME IS IN EARLY DEVELOPMENT SO THERE ARE ONLY 2 STAGES. PLEASE REPORT ANY BUGS OR GLITCHES IN THE COMMENTS.
